ERP DB Copy
===========

Clone a Tryton or OpenERP database to new database (add _copia).

Installing
----------

See INSTALL

Package Contents
----------------

  bin/
      Program.

  erpdbcopy/
      ERP DB Copy sources.

License
-------

See LICENSE

Copyright
---------

See COPYRIGHT

Example to use
--------------

    $ erpdbcopy -u user -p password -d dbname -s server -e trytond

Server option is optional. If don't use it, get name from dbname

Example crontab
---------------

    30 1 * * * /usr/local/bin/erpdbcopy -u user -p password -d dbname -s server -e trytond

Log file
--------

    /var/log/erpdbcopy.log
